APPROVED

BY THE FDA IN JANUARY 2004 AND LAUNCHED IN THE U.S.

IN JUNE 2004, IS AN INHALED TREATMENT FOR THE

LONG-TERM, ONCE-DAILY MAINTENANCE TREATMENT OF

BRONCHOSPASM ASSOCIATED WITH COPD.

SPIRIVA

HAS ALSO

