MOST OF OUR OPERATIONS ARE AFFECTED BY FEDERAL, STATE AND/OR LOCAL ENVIRONMENTAL LAWS. WE

HAVE MADE, AND INTEND TO CONTINUE TO MAKE, NECESSARY EXPENDITURES FOR COMPLIANCE WITH APPLICABLE

LAWS. WE ALSO ARE CLEANING UP ENVIRONMENTAL CONTAMINATION FROM PAST INDUSTRIAL ACTIVITY AT CERTAIN

SITES (SEE NOTE 17 TO OUR CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS,

LEGAL PROCEEDINGS AND CONTINGENCIES,

IN OUR 2004 FINANCIAL REPORT). AS A RESULT, WE INCURRED CAPITAL AND OPERATIONAL EXPENDITURES IN

